  <p>
    <strong>For composers</strong> - I have already completed the composers agreement&nbsp;<%= f.check_box :pub_licence_already %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>For performers</strong> - I have provided SOUNZ with a list of previous performances of New Zealand music &nbsp;<%= f.check_box :pub_licence_forms_send %>
  </p>

  <p>
    Are you a member of CANZ?&nbsp;<%= f.check_box :member_canz %>
  </p>

  <p>
    Are you a member of APRA?&nbsp;<%= f.check_box :member_apra %>
  </p>

<h2>Other Contact Information</h2>
  <p>
    <span class="instruction">Please note any other contact details that may assist us to stay in touch with you and promote your music.</span><br>
    <%= f.text_area :other_contact, :cols => standard_edit_cols, :rows => standard_edit_rows %>
  </p>
